Up to date as of 9/1/2008.

Issue #8 is the unnumbered one-shot "Segue to Destruction" which serves as a prelude to the 4-part "Calamari Rising" story.  I haven&#039;t found an official numbered #8 so I assume my numbering is correct.

None of these were ripped by me; all were found elsewhere.  If you like it, buy it.
